metadata.name: Enrique el Hermoso
metadata.description:
Hi my name is Enrique. I'm a 2 year old cockatiel. I'm a musician I know 7 songs an more than 10 annoying noices. I love seeds and preenings. I have two female humans. I love caos and bitting earphones or any cable in the house.

  The artist who created this work is a good friend of mine, he is not into NFTs. I have your authorization for minting this piece. This piece is a gift and is not available for sale.
